            <description>&lt;p align="left"&gt;
	The Ultrasound World VI conference, launching May 10, will feature four days of presentations, workshops, classes and an&amp;nbsp;optional CMRP exam with a strong emphasis on application based case histories using ultrasound as part of a profitable predictive maintenance strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
