	A true networking event, presenters will be able to share their wisdom and technical insights, helping attendees optimize the performance of this important PdM technology. With the addition of Dr. James Neale, an internationally recognized industrial research analyst and Senior Research Fellow at the University of Waikato in New Zealand and his presentation on &amp;quot;Monitoring of Variable Speed Bearings Using Structure Borne Ultrasound&amp;quot;, Ultrasound World has truly become among the most useful conferences for global reliability insight and education.&lt;/p&gt;
